title: Bitcoin Depot FY2024 EPS Estimate Boosted by Northland Capmk
description: Bitcoin Depot Inc. (NASDAQ:BTM – Free Report) – Stock analysts at Northland Capmk upped their FY2024 EPS estimates for shares of Bitcoin Depot in a research note issued on Wednesday, January 22nd. Northland Capmk analyst M. Grondahl now expects that the company will earn $0.02 per share for the year, up from their previous forecast […]
